  "subject": "Fix to send an existing request id to AAI",
  "commit_message": " Fix to send an existing request id to AAI\n\n When SO module is calling AAI Rest services, it is always passing new\n random UUID. As per EELF guidelines, request id is used for\n indentifying a transaction across ONAP components. This fix checks\n whether Request ID is present in MDC, if yes pass same else create new,\n set new Request Id in MDC and pass that to AAI.\n\nChange-Id: I7ede85039f291b07d89d983022eb5a0b7ebe79d7\nIssue-ID: SO-78\nSigned-off-by: anupmarathe <anup.marathe@amdocs.com>\n",
